This is a simple web application for creating and viewing forums for retro gamers!. Please note that this project is a work in progress and may contain bugs and unfinished features.

## Installation

1. Download the project from the GitHub repository.
2. Extract the downloaded ZIP file.

## Prerequisites

- Python 3.x
- Flask
- SQLite

## Setup

1. Open a terminal or command prompt.
2. Navigate to the extracted project directory.

### Create a Virtual Environment (Optional)

It is recommended to create a virtual environment to isolate the project dependencies. You can use `venv` or any other virtual environment tool of your choice.

# Create a virtual environment
python3 -m venv venv

# Activate the virtual environment
source venv/bin/activate  # Linux/macOS
venv\Scripts\activate  # Windows
Install Dependencies
Install the required Python packages using pip.

Copy code
pip install -r requirements.txt

Usage
In the terminal or command prompt, navigate to the project directory.
Run the following command to start the Flask development server:

Copy code
python app.py
Open a web browser and visit http://localhost:5000 to access the application.

Known Issues
This project is a work in progress and may contain bugs.
Some features are not fully implemented.
Security measures are not implemented (e.g., authentication, authorization).
Performance optimizations are not considered in this stage.

Contributing
Contributions are welcome! If you encounter any bugs or have suggestions for improvements, please create an issue or submit a pull request.
